channel.title: Chase - lagrangian [Experimental, Drill n Bass, Soundtrack]
channel.description: Good day everyone! I'm proud to present my serious song that I've made on Auxy. Check it out here. :tada: I would love to know what your honest opinion is on it. Furthermore, I really don't know what genre this song is other than perhaps some sort of science fiction-y soundtrack-like song. (I guess that makes sense considering my growing interest in cyberpunk.) I'd love to know what your take is on that as well.

item.title: Chase - lagrangian [Experimental, Drill n Bass, Soundtrack]
item.dc:creator: iammane
item.description:
I like it! You’re getting sounds out of Auxy that I’m not quite sure how you’re doing… in a good way! Overall it’s got this electronic industrial sound I’m digging. I definitely can see (hear?) the sci-fi / cyberpunk influence too.

Keep it up!
